database.query: SELECT SMF30JBN , JESNUM , SMF30STM , SMF30STN , SMF30PGM , SMF30RUD , BEGINTIME , ENDTIME , ROUND(CPUTIME, 2) AS CPUTIME , ZIPTM , ELAPSED , COALESCE(CONDCODE,'0') as condcode , DISKIO , DISKIOTM  , SMF30CL8 as class   FROM CR00515.EPV30_23_intrvl WHERE SYSTEM = ? AND SMF30WID = 'JES2' AND SMF30JBN= ? AND JESNUM= ? ORDER BY SMF30STN, BEGINTIME;
